main event: A UFO was observed by a student at the University of South Alabama on October 13, 1966, at 0730 hours.
interesting points: The object was circular and approximately 25-30 feet in diameter, Observed for about 5 full minutes, The UFO emitted a faint humming sound, The object departed to the north after performing straight line maneuvers, The weather was clear and cloudless during the observation.
sighted object: circular UFO with a highly polished appearance and no observable openings
witness description: An 18-year-old freshman student at the University of South Alabama and her History Professor.
